flowchart TB
    A[50 Hz raster IRQ] --> B[Music driver wakes]
    B --> C{Is this voice playing a chord?}
    C -- yes --> D[Read arp_step]
    D --> E[Load note from 3-entry table]
    E --> F[Write to D400 / D401]
    F --> G[Advance arp_step mod 3]
    C -- no --> H[Hold current note]
    G --> I[Move to next voice]
    H --> I
    I --> J[Return from IRQ]
    J --> A

    style F fill:#cfe8d4,stroke:#2a7a3a,color:#000
    style E fill:#d6e0f5,stroke:#3a5aa2,color:#000
    style G fill:#f7d6cf,stroke:#a23a2a,color:#000
